Here, music is born not for a purpose, but for some kind of reason.
The role of the audience can be felt more at concerts, where the influence on each other already works, but this only lies in the intangible changes of the moment.
However, I have noticed that if you try to please the audience, then you are no longer interesting.
hvg.hu: To what extent do you plan to follow Yonderboi&#39;s example?
He works solo and built his career further west than us.
Zs.B.: We don&#39;t really follow his path, regardless of the fact that sometimes they try to explain this in our music.
